		<th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" height="25" width="100">&nbsp;Author</th><th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" width="85%">&nbsp;Thread: Mezzing, Lulling, Looting - Questions From A Curious Bard</th>
	</tr><tr>
		<td class="PanelBody" nowrap="nowrap" valign="Top" width="150"><table border="0">
			<tr>
				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Cyanu is not online. Last active: 3/25/2004 4:56:55 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Cyanu">Cyanu</a><br></td>
